{"tid":1560715,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"點解無人留意我地下一代將唔需要學廣東話？！","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T07:27:06.000Z","uid":232841,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ebbd9a6f38e407352c34c0d8e462700a19136c47","tid":1560715,"uid":232841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:18:10.000Z","msg":"政府出左諮詢文件：<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2FTF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWX4IrTm65yM4JHcsBx4PGkA%3D&h=bba3a3b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n建議取消中文課<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聆聽</span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">口試</span><br />\n<br />\n美其名減輕學生壓力<br />\n實際幫班大陸學生破除障礙<br />\n<br />\n我地依家辛辛苦苦搞時代革命 <span style=\"color: red;\">都需要未來新一代延續</span><br />\n如果下一代都唔係自己人，我地辛辛苦苦建立既嘢將<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全盤失去！</span></span><br />\n<br />\ntaskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk 一人一信<br />\n唔好懶 好重要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vpnr7tY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVpnr7tY.png&h=473af738&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b090db91a649355edd037117957b89efa9c2d2ae","tid":1560715,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:18:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3f6a81258d0a6ef4153efec3a8eede6cd5f2a662","tid":1560715,"uid":138934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ad3a1fc50e4c93d09eacb3d97b3f12b7dd9465","tid":1560715,"uid":58958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:21:35.000Z","msg":"【保民聯】建制保皇 建設保民 香港值得更好的建設派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560300</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2edu5dD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2edu5dD.png&h=f7e4a997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"616f4e0c9d3e1d309b55c01741771ec9bafb0b18","tid":1560715,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"【保民聯】建制保皇 建設保民 香港值得更好的建設派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560300</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2edu5dD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2edu5dD.png&h=f7e4a997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d567bbb599cc415cf6c5a84b6ec4aac2f0aaf5b9","tid":1560715,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"有無範本send"},{"pid":"ad33261a292a32c2924678ea5307ba7612534aef","tid":1560715,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:22:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1588f10aa1caa9c55dddf5b17ae35496616d0c1e","tid":1560715,"uid":303465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"推 一人一個email"},{"pid":"74880cf2592ba547bdc839c50d8c4862d61b1aca","tid":1560715,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"推推攞埋"},{"pid":"cbc83b19a656fbcda9f6ce577f5ff4085428fb6f","tid":1560715,"uid":34020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:36:46.000Z","msg":"人人有責推post上熱門"},{"pid":"4ef381c8faa9f57db7bbfa4bec4e9cfb66187859","tid":1560715,"uid":285826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:54:32.000Z","msg":"香港人係香港生活，點可以聽說冇廣東話?冇左不如唔好係香港生活。邊個弱智仔諗要刪?"},{"pid":"158446ff40c42e2ba7a57eb2092338ca435753aa","tid":1560715,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wx2Po00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwx2Po00.jpg&h=3157bb59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0fcaf8256ef100f123cd3f16b8ac04d600fa8d5d","tid":1560715,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:26:00.000Z","msg":"⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠<br />\n大家幫幫手send email，明天16號就係實施普教中咨詢deadline，通過左就再無粵語教學‼<br />\n⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠<br />\n<br />\n廣東話始終係我地由細到大嘅語言，大家一起幫手捍衛母語🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼<br />\n<br />\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n<br />\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299<br />\n<br />\n致專責小組成員：<br />\n<br />\n本人為香港市民，有聞 貴組於6月28日文件中提出刪去文憑試聆聽及說話考卷，本人強烈反對，原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n一，掌握母語不等於能以母語表達，說話要言之有物、出口成文，除了要豐富的詞彙，亦要有清晰的表達方式，說話卷的核心價值在於檢視學生在日常用語之外，能否有效建構論點展開討論，而廢除後則無地方訓練學生這頂基本能力。<br />\n<br />\n二，掌握母語不等於能理解別人話語內容，聆聽別人的說話可以訓練學生將對話精煉的能力，亦即是捕捉重點的能力，假如廢除，恐怕學生會失去一個練習的平台，無法與人有效溝通。<br />\n<br />\n三，以語言系公開試ielts雅思為例，考核學生英語水平以讀聽寫說四考卷，尤其是以說話難度最高，一向是該考試衡量英語高水平者的好標準，如今 貴組研廢除聆、說二卷，猶如自斷一臂。<br />\n<br />\n綜合以上及眾多學者之言，冀 貴組於此項教育改革方向予於重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n祝<br />\n工作順利"},{"pid":"5cd31d4e9a47438cda946eb6d70a74535aa992f4","tid":1560715,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:17:14.000Z","msg":"Push!!"},{"pid":"5091819a015b7bf700453fa8e005bd1fb238fc67","tid":1560715,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36079520151d500da17f839df3ba39f19252ba5","tid":1560715,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"今次輸左<br />\n係咪都冇粵語啦<br />\n相反今次贏<br />\n我地改做英文/俄文/德文/火星文都得啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92a6afc3f93be49521569ca5420b11217ffded6","tid":1560715,"uid":211323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de84138a4909487055c20b4821773f0d0ececfe3","tid":1560715,"uid":56444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d36079520151d500da17f839df3ba39f19252ba5","tid":1560715,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"今次輸左<br />\n係咪都冇粵語啦<br />\n相反今次贏<br />\n我地改做英文/俄文/德文/火星文都得啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"改叫香港話 香港文"},{"pid":"606049c898edc9b1c789c840773991ae77debcc4","tid":1560715,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de84138a4909487055c20b4821773f0d0ececfe3","tid":1560715,"uid":56444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d36079520151d500da17f839df3ba39f19252ba5","tid":1560715,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"今次輸左<br />\n係咪都冇粵語啦<br />\n相反今次贏<br />\n我地改做英文/俄文/德文/火星文都得啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"改叫香港話 香港文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦<br />\n我既意思係，今次輸左就乜都冇<br />\n香港一定會俾大陸清洗<br />\n所以，努力打贏個主線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ceed4a604d052f5375b77c9a2530e5e293be17","tid":1560715,"uid":56444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"606049c898edc9b1c789c840773991ae77debcc4","tid":1560715,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de84138a4909487055c20b4821773f0d0ececfe3","tid":1560715,"uid":56444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d36079520151d500da17f839df3ba39f19252ba5","tid":1560715,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:21:09.000Z","msg":"今次輸左<br />\n係咪都冇粵語啦<br />\n相反今次贏<br />\n我地改做英文/俄文/德文/火星文都得啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"改叫香港話 香港文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦<br />\n我既意思係，今次輸左就乜都冇<br />\n香港一定會俾大陸清洗<br />\n所以，努力打贏個主線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"啱 教育係長期 但而家香港問題係逼切好多"},{"pid":"4135009164b07e1516e09845dab93f94d437597b","tid":1560715,"uid":137874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"sent and<br />\npush"},{"pid":"8f727d40407741609400c98a3aadf00689b4d72c","tid":1560715,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T07:09:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f295552c57fd281bd81231820f07b32ccf74ff58","tid":1560715,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"敬啟者  <br />\n<br />\n本人是香港市民，從網上得知  貴組於6月28日文件中提出欲刪去文憑試當中中文科的聆聽及說話考卷，本人表示強烈反對，原因如下：  <br />\n<br />\n一，說話考卷能夠考核考生以母語即時將心中所想以口述的形式去組織和表達的能力<br />\n<br />\n二，聆聽考卷能夠考核考生以母語邊聆聽、邊理解別人說話內容，即時捕捉重點的能力<br />\n<br />\n三，以上兩方面的能力，都是即時與其他人互相溝通所必須，無論在日常生活中以及日後工作上都是必備，而聆聽及說話考卷能夠提供平台去考核考生於即時面對面溝通的能力<br />\n<br />\n四，而閱讀卷和寫作卷是純文字的考核，使用的是書面語而非日常溝通的口語，不能完全反映考生以廣東話與人面對面以口語溝通的即時表現<br />\n<br />\n五，再者，日常對話時說話一出口就無法收回，而閱讀卷和寫作卷的答案，可以在考試結束時間前再三修改，並不能考核考生即時以口語面對面溝通的能力<br />\n<br />\n六，綜合以上理由，不同考卷的考核內容的性質完全不同，如只有閱讀卷和寫作卷，而沒有聆聽及說話考卷，是無法從全方位的去考核考生的實際語言能力<br />\n<br />\n因此，文憑試當中中文科的聆聽及說話考卷有其存在的必要，本人強烈反對取消，敬希 貴組能基於以上各項理由考慮，並保留聆聽及說話考卷。  <br />\n<br />\n此致"}]}